{"tid":1500992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠用緊拖字訣","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T02:54:01.000Z","uid":31311,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67fe1ab71d4e7e76348e032951b4b2d5a6af4ad1","tid":1500992,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"唔好屌我住，雖然柒婆都拖咗咁多個月，但係我有幾個更新嘅論點，睇完唔認同先再屌。<br />\n用一個放軟嘅態度黎面對將來嘅示威，並且將所有社會問題推曬落義士到，令中間派或者淺黃派開始不滿。<br />\n<br />\n1. D狗依加發tg嘅數量減少，純粹由勇武手足擺陣，營造手足堵塞道路，衝擊狗屋。<br />\n<br />\n2. 黨鐵不經任何示威嘅鐵路站，營造出交通不便係示威者問題，如果冇示威就唔會封站。<br />\n<br />\n3. 出咗大大小小嘅禁制令，係令到大家認為好多野都唔方便，香港人最討厭嘅野係唔方便。<br />\n<br />\n但係依加我地依加要做嘅係大力文宣，所有不方便、混亂，其實都只不過係政府制造出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"e099578078352f2e869dfe0deb86467cadf034b6","tid":1500992,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:15:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23b81db5a5bd4f88f5c68b8591a3194f1f689d6c","tid":1500992,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:15:28.000Z","msg":"大大力咁推"},{"pid":"15c6e9acd089eb66e2ebc4a520ded5bcb1806e3d","tid":1500992,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"大家有咩建議拆"},{"pid":"737202568453cf14ff3fc490667339e5ec8b18a4","tid":1500992,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:18:08.000Z","msg":"點拖？<br />\n國慶就到<br />\n<br />\n示威活動 <br />\n集中五六日"},{"pid":"ae0b4d0fdb540d5da7ad0c488dc1d339147831e3","tid":1500992,"uid":31311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"十連推"},{"pid":"c2f88b8941c5738aea6f4205b8ec13e27de6fc1f","tid":1500992,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"拖到美國國會復會囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我OK"},{"pid":"c81db42eaccc70f9d9461bc4d30fe6